text: Naskia is a genus of sea snails, marine gastropod mollusks in the family Horaiclavidae. ==Species== Species within the genus Naskia include: * Naskia axiplicata Sysoev & Ivanov, 1985 ==References== * Sysoev, A. V., and D. L. Ivanov. "Nex Taxa of the Family Turridae (Gastropoda, Toxoglossa) from the Naska-ridge (Southeast Pacific)." Zoologichesky Zhurnal 64.2 (1985): 194-205. ==External links== * Tucker, J.K. 2004 Catalog of recent and fossil turrids (Mollusca: Gastropoda). Zootaxa 682:1-1295.
